eqAcacMib.name: eqAcacMib
eqAcacMib.contactinfo: Jas Parmar Equipe Communications 100 Nagog Park Acton MA 01720
eqAcacMib.description: This is the Equipe ACAC MIB module.

eqAcacViTable.name: eqAcacViTable
eqAcacViTable.description: This table contains stats for an ACAC logical port.

eqAcacViEntry.name: eqAcacViEntry
eqAcacViEntry.description: An ACAC logical port stats entry.

eqAcacViIfIndex.name: eqAcacViIfIndex
eqAcacViIfIndex.description: The ifIndex for the logical port.

eqAcacViStartingBw.name: eqAcacViStartingBw
eqAcacViStartingBw.description: The initial amount of bandwidth allocated to this virtual interface (in cells per second).

eqAcacViConsumedBw.name: eqAcacViConsumedBw
eqAcacViConsumedBw.description: The amount of bandwidth consumed by existing circuits (in cells per second).

eqAcacViInConsideredCcts.name: eqAcacViInConsideredCcts
eqAcacViInConsideredCcts.description: The number of circuits that CAC has been asked to consider for admission.

eqAcacViInRejectedCcts.name: eqAcacViInRejectedCcts
eqAcacViInRejectedCcts.description: The number of circuits that CAC has been asked to consider for admission for which sufficient resources have not been available. Hence the circuit was rejected.

eqAcacViInActiveCcts.name: eqAcacViInActiveCcts
eqAcacViInActiveCcts.description: The number of currently active circuits

eqAcacViInReservedCcts.name: eqAcacViInReservedCcts
eqAcacViInReservedCcts.description: The number of circuits that CAC has reserved resources, but is waiting for a commit.

eqAcacViOutConsideredCcts.name: eqAcacViOutConsideredCcts
eqAcacViOutConsideredCcts.description: The number of circuits that CAC has been asked to consider for admission.

eqAcacViOutRejectedCcts.name: eqAcacViOutRejectedCcts
eqAcacViOutRejectedCcts.description: The number of circuits that CAC has been asked to consider for admission for which sufficient resources have not been available. Hence the circuit was rejected.

eqAcacViOutActiveCcts.name: eqAcacViOutActiveCcts
eqAcacViOutActiveCcts.description: The number of currently active circuits.

eqAcacViOutReservedCcts.name: eqAcacViOutReservedCcts
eqAcacViOutReservedCcts.description: The number of circuits that CAC has reserved resources, but is waiting for a commit.

eqAcacViServCatTable.name: eqAcacViServCatTable
eqAcacViServCatTable.description: This table contains stats per ATM Service Category for an ACAC logical port.

eqAcacViServCatEntry.name: eqAcacViServCatEntry
eqAcacViServCatEntry.description: An ACAC logical port service category stats entry.

eqAcacViServCatIfIndex.name: eqAcacViServCatIfIndex
eqAcacViServCatIfIndex.description: The ifIndex for the logical port.

eqAcacViServCatServiceCategory.name: eqAcacViServCatServiceCategory
eqAcacViServCatServiceCategory.description: The Service Category that this instance in the table describes.

eqAcacViServCatConsumedBw.name: eqAcacViServCatConsumedBw
eqAcacViServCatConsumedBw.description: The amount of bandwidth currently considered in use by this service category for the purposes of CAC calculations. Note that this does not represent actual traffic utilitization.

eqAcacViServCatActiveCcts.name: eqAcacViServCatActiveCcts
eqAcacViServCatActiveCcts.description: The number of active circuits for this service category on this virtual interface.
